  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Norvos\" title=\"Norvos\"><img alt=\"Norvos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5a/Norvos.svg/50px-Norvos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5a/Norvos.svg/75px-Norvos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5a/Norvos.svg/100px-Norvos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Doro Golathis</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Norvos\" title=\"Norvos\"><img alt=\"Norvos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5a/Norvos.svg/50px-Norvos.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5a/Norvos.svg/75px-Norvos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5a/Norvos.svg/100px-Norvos.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Norvos\" title=\"Norvos\">Norvos</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Doro Golathis</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Norvos\" title=\"Norvos\">Norvoshi</a> historian. He stated there are remnants of <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rhoynish\">Rhoynish</a> outposts in <a href=\"/index.php/Andalos\" title=\"Andalos\">Andalos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_the_coming_of_the_andals.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#